          "TITLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Resonance parameters from neutron radiative",
                " capture in U-238"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "LINAC"
                ],
                "institute": "2ZZZGEL"
              },
              "free_text": [
                "  The CBNM 60 MeV electron linear",
                " accelerator. The nominal resolution varied between",
                " 20 nsec/m and 1 nsec/m for different energy ranges."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".Photo-neutrons from a natural uranium target",
                " moderated by a polyethylene sheet."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".Depleted uranium, 0.2% 92-U-235, with thicknesses of",
                " 3.06E-3 atoms/b and 1.01E-2 atoms/b."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "    Time of flight, flight path = 60 m."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MOXR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "    A modified Moxon Rae detector."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "BF3"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " .B-F(3) counter for neutron spectrum.",
                ".Boron-10 slab viewed by a Na-I crystal for",
                " neutron spectrum."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "AREA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "    Together with the CBNM transmission data",
                " by Carraro, Kolar,70Helsinki,1,403,(CN-26/17),",
                " (Subentries 20115.002-005), a combined area analysis",
                " method was applied to get the resonance parameters",
                " in the energy range from 50 eV to 1 keV using the",
                " Tacasi-program (froehner, Ga-6906(1966)).",
                " This program chooses the resonance parameters by means",
                " of a Least Square Method if no unique intersection",
                " in the gamma(n) - gamma(gamma) plane was obtained."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "MONITOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": null,
                "reaction": {
                  "code": "92-U-238(N,G)92-U-239,,SIG,,RES",
                  "code_unit": [
                    {
                      "unit": "92-U-238(N,G)92-U-239,,SIG,,RES",
                      "field": {
                        "reaction": "92-U-238(N,G)92-U-239",
                        "target": "92-U-238",
                        "projectile": "N",
                        "process": "G",
                        "product": "92-U-239",
                        "quantity": ",SIG,,RES",
                        "data_type": null,
                        "general_quantity_modifier": null,
                        "quantity_236": ",SIG,,RES"
                      }
                    }
                  ],
                  "unit_combination": "(%)"
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                " The 6.67 eV resonance was used for absolute",
                " determination of the product of detector-efficiency",
                " and neutron-flux."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".No evidence for an intermediate structure in the",
                " total radiative widths of U-238 was observed in the",
                " present experiment.",
                ".Resonance energies are taken from G.Carraro and",
                " W.Kolar, Helsinki conference 1970 vol.1, p.403.",
                ".The capture data are raw data not suited for",
                " publication, (letter from Kolar, 22 February 1971)."
              ]
            }
          ],
